{"tid":804438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔11年後再「走塑」 麥當勞逢周一列「無飲管日」","createTime":"2018-09-03T04:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T07:48:48.000Z","uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e136d015f87931f7d1e1c56804a851ad04711099","tid":804438,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"快餐店肯德基（KFC）上月宣佈，香港和澳門全線分店將正式停用塑膠飲管和杯蓋以減少浪費。香港麥當勞今日亦表示，為響應環保，全線麥當勞和McCaf&eacute;今日起，每逢周一實行「無飲管星期一」，但使用管形匙羹之飲品不在此限。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180903/large/1535944185_8111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180903%2Flarge%2F1535944185_8111.jpg&h=e5198afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥當勞表示，逢周一麥當勞會清空飲管箱，亦不會主動派發飲管，如有需要可向職員索取。早於2007年6月，麥當勞亦曾將每月的第2及第4個星期一定為「無飲管日」，當日全線餐廳會把飲管收起，但在2008年開始就改為自願性質，變相將活動取消。"},{"pid":"e6d8d540d84819dcdc3fb08ccd41c1b3222d5c7f","tid":804438,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e681217910b1637302b89d1a8cfa4c88cba5a0","tid":804438,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bb4b73211a65e9b35b2026713e9fe69bf8f0b7","tid":804438,"uid":7688,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"班人腦裝屎<br />\n唔換個杯點樣飲"},{"pid":"23ee4ef2aac54fa3cd25ac0b3226e8f58e943770","tid":804438,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"照問佢拎飲管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3daf7d2c0ffefa9373a1f93f8d4f1147763590","tid":804438,"uid":60169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"而家食緊m記。 啲客叫班m 記員工比飲筒， 班員工係咁話冇飲筒日冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile